Requirment 

Internet Cafe
	 are places that have computers available, usually for a fee, that you can use to go online.
 	a business enterprise that provides internet access, digital and computer related services to its customers 
 Services offered by internet cafes:
  • Internet Access
   • Computer Rentals
   • Printing
   • Computer Repair and Maintenance
    • Digital Literacy and Training
     • Computer Related Services such as encoding and data recovery.

Equipment in an Internet Cafe
	Computer
	Router
	Switch 
	Printer
	HeadSet
	